task.summary: Fixed bad implementation of > and < operators.
Defined the location lookup a bit better.
Added header files to cmake project so that my editor indexes them.
Formally wrote down the XOR-closest binary search algorithm.
Wrote the ContactsSet container to keep track of a list of contacts and query them efficiently.

Performed some major refactoring to apply dependency inversion principle using dependency injection, made coupling weaker, etc... Renamed all headers to end in .hpp Replaced the Packet factory methods with constructors. Added documentation Other changes
Seperated runUnitTests into core tests and full tests.
Fixed ContactsSet not correctly handling duplicates.
